  "title": "Enrolled Nurse (Office Hours)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description: </strong><br />We are seeking a detail-oriented and organized Clinic Assistant to support daily operations at our healthcare clinic. The role involves managing administrative tasks, coordinating patient services, and ensuring efficient clinic operations. <br /><br /><strong>Key responsibilities: </strong><br />•\tProvide and evaluate clinical services and nursing care rendered to patients <br />•\tPerform services such as procedure & treatments to improve the general comfort and well being of patients <br />•\tDispensing of medications <br />•\tCommunicate and coordinate patient care with other healthcare providers <br />•\tHandle general administrative duties <br />•\tProvide patients with basic patient education related to their clinical condition <br />•\tRecord and report information in a clear and concise manner on the nursing care or clinical services rendered to the patient <br />•\tAssist the medical officer, nursing staff or other healthcare personnel in the treatment & examination of the patient <br />•\tPerforms phlebotomy or blood taking services under minimum supervision•\tAssist patients in the various clinical or auxiliary departments as assigned<br />•\tProvide guidance and orientation to clinic assistant and others <br />•\tParticipate in all activities related to the smooth running of the clinic <br />•\tMaintain a safe & clean environment for the patients at all times <br />•\tPerform any other tasks as assigned by the Clinic Manager <br />•\tPreferred to start immediately <br /><br /><strong>Requirements: </strong><br />•\t2 years related experience <br />•\tSingapore Nursing Board Practising Certificate is a MUST <br />•\tStrong team player <br />•\t5.5 days work week (Monday to Friday; Saturday - half day) <br />•\tLocation: Buona Vista/Orchard</p>",
